<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> Harpham, Geoffrey. “Beneath and Beyond the Crisis of the Humanities,” <a href="/wiki/New_Literary_History" title="New Literary History"><i>New Literary History</i></a> 36 (2005), 21-36.</li>
