<li id="cite_note-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27" title="">^</a></b> ""Theory," Anti-Theory, and Empirical Criticism," <i>Biopoetics: Evolutionary Explorations in the Arts</i>, Brett Cooke and Frederick Turner, eds., Lexington, Kentucky: ICUS Books, 1999, pp. 144-145. 152.</li>
